const options = [

    { value: "16-20", label: "16-20 Years of experience" },
    { value: "21-25", label: "21-25 Years of experience" },
    { value: "26-30", label: "26-30 Years of experience" },
    { value: "30+", label: "30+ Years of experience" },
];

export {
    yearOptions,
    options
